DE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>Brell Server<br>&quot;But it conned BLUE!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utalvin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talvin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 65<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/5/01 8:32:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathholyswordsandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2922.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Post 50 Pally and fa/fd question</span><hr size=1> Garthin,<br><br>Just curious, what other weapons out there for Paladins are near equivelent to a FD? Only one that comes to mind is Natures Defender. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uomenn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Omenn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 242<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/5/01 8:43:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathholyswordsandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2922.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Post 50 Pally and fa/fd question</span><hr size=1> In damage delay some of the DN etc weapons are near equivalent. But the FD gives a ton of stats, AC, the ability to bash and a proc. FD in my opinion is much better.<br><br>My suggestion to you is to level up, play and have fun. And if some day you finally come across both book halves then that's great! Don't let the FA/FD stop you from leveling. <p><TABLE><TR><TD><font face="Arial, Verdana Helvetica" size="-2"><a href="mailto:omenn@valorblade.com">o m e n n @ v a l o r b l a d e 